parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the CVT transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, jerk, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or fails to accelerate
the transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle makes unusual noises
such as grinding or whining sounds
and the transmission warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or hesitation can cause the vehicle to lose power, jerk, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle hesitates or fails to accelerate
the vehicle makes unusual noises
such as grinding or whining sounds
and the transmission warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loss of acceleration can cause the vehicle to fail to respond to the driver's inputs, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to accelerate or hesitates when accelerating
the vehicle makes unusual noises
such as grinding or whining sounds
and the transmission warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in a crash
airbag light is on or flashing
passenger airbag light stays on even when occupied
seat belt light is on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunction of the airbag system can lead to false warnings, failure to deploy, or unintended deployment, which can cause accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Airbag light is on or flashing
passenger airbag light stays on even when occupied
seat belt light is on
airbag warning message appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake failure can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
car won't stop
brake failure warning message appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The TAKATA airbag recall is a safety issue that can cause airbags to deploy improperly, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag recall notice
airbag light is on or flashing
passenger airbag light stays on even when occupied.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering light comes on
the power steering fails to function
the steering wheel becomes hard to turn
the vehicle is difficult to maneuver
and the power steering warning indicator illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering wheel comes off
the steering wheel assembly cracks
and the left side of the steering wheel piece breaks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the traction control system can cause the vehicle to lose traction, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or sways to one side
the vehicle feels out of control
and the vehicle's stability is compromised.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
and the vehicle's stability is compromised.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic power steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering fails to function
the power steering light comes on
and the vehicle is difficult to maneuver.
